definitions.definition: A person who installs thatch as a roofing material.
A device which removes dead grass clippings from a lawn . (Technically a dethatcher , often a lawnmower attachment.)

main_definition: A person who installs thatch as a roofing material.
secondary_definitions: A device which removes dead grass clippings from a lawn . (Technically a dethatcher , often a lawnmower attachment.)
